data.description: Welcome to Great Road Condominiums in the charming town of Acton! Seize the opportunity to own this fantastic condo at a great price. This inviting unit presents a comfortable living space, a designated dining area, and a spacious walk-in closet, providing ample storage for your belongings. Enjoy the convenience of condo living with amenities such as the pool, tennis court and maintenance taken care of for you. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a piece of Acton at an unbeatable price! Open houses this weekend Saturday & Sunday 12-2
